{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.360", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrter Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.320", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.840", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.520", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir stehen am Beginn der Haushaltsberatungen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.840", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch f\u00fcr diesen Haushaltsentwurf gilt sicherlich das Struck\u2019sche Gesetz: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.760", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kein Gesetz kommt aus dem Parlament so heraus, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.560", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie es eingebracht worden ist.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "27.880", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir werden sehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "27.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.120", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie der Haushalt Anfang Juli dann aussehen wird."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.800", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vieles wurde bereits angesprochen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.240", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der Bereich G\u00fcterverkehr, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "38.360", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Transportlogistik jedoch nur am Rande. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "38.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "42.320", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich m\u00f6chte in meiner Rede mein Augenmerk auf die Arbeits- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "42.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "47.160", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Wettbewerbsbedingungen im Stra\u00dfeng\u00fctertransport richten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "47.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.760", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Da k\u00f6nnen wir mit relativ geringen Haushaltsmitteln, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.480", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie ich finde, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "51.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "53.320", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "vieles bewegen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "53.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "56.280", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben im Koalitionsvertrag verabredet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "56.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "63.200", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir Sozialdumping und Sozialbetrug auf unseren Stra\u00dfen bek\u00e4mpfen wollen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "63.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "66.200", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dabei spielen Kontrollbeh\u00f6rden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "66.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "68.000", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auch das Bundesamt f\u00fcr G\u00fcterverkehr, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "68.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "70.640", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sicherlich eine zentrale Rolle."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "70.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "74.080", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben im Koalitionsvertrag festgehalten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "74.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "76.320", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir diese Beh\u00f6rde besser ausstatten wollen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "76.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "86.680", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Transport und Logistik vor allem auf der Stra\u00dfe haben als Wirtschaftsfaktoren und mit Blick auf Arbeitspl\u00e4tze eine enorme Relevanz f\u00fcr unsere Volkswirtschaft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "86.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "89.040", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und die Branche w\u00e4chst stetig. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "89.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "95.040", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Wachstum des Stra\u00dfeng\u00fcterverkehrs liegt seit Jahren \u00fcber dem Wirtschaftswachstum in Deutschland. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "95.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "101.880", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Allein 2017 nahmen die Transportleistungen auf der Stra\u00dfe um 2,6\u00a0Prozent zu. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "101.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "109.080", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Von diesem Wachstum profitieren vor allem auch im Ausland ans\u00e4ssige Speditionen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "109.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "114.320", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Verkehrsleistung deutscher Lkws wuchs 2016 um 0,6\u00a0Prozent, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "114.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "117.160", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "2017 um 1,2\u00a0Prozent. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "117.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "118.360", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zum Vergleich: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "118.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "124.280", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ausl\u00e4ndische Mitbewerber legten gleichzeitig um knapp 3\u00a0Prozent bzw. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "124.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "125.560", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "5\u00a0Prozent zu. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "125.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "131.400", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Verkehrsleistung aus Kabotage stieg in Deutschland 2016 im Vergleich zum Vorjahr sogar um \u00fcber 30\u00a0Prozent. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "131.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "137.680", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Noch vor zehn Jahren hatten zwei von drei Lkws auf deutschen Stra\u00dfen ein einheimisches Kennzeichen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "137.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "140.800", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Heute liegt der Anteil der ausl\u00e4ndischen Lkws bei 45\u00a0Prozent, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "140.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "146.520", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und f\u00fcnf von sechs dieser Lkws stammen aus unseren osteurop\u00e4ischen Nachbarl\u00e4ndern."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "146.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "147.880", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nun kann man sagen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "147.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "152.920", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das sei in einem europ\u00e4ischen Binnenmarkt mit freiem Marktzugang normal, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "152.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "157.320", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die osteurop\u00e4ischen Anbieter seien eben wettbewerbsf\u00e4higer. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "157.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "158.840", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Selbstverst\u00e4ndlich\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "158.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "159.640", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und dies betone ich\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "159.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "164.480", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "will niemand vern\u00fcnftigerweise den Binnenmarkt infrage stellen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "164.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "165.720", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir brauchen ihn. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "165.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "169.280", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Allerdings d\u00fcrfen wir nicht die Augen davor verschlie\u00dfen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "169.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "174.120", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass osteurop\u00e4ische Speditionen mit Dumpingpreisen arbeiten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "174.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "179.400", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie zahlen keine fairen L\u00f6hne und f\u00fchren auch keine Sozialabgaben ab, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "179.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "181.480", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die mit unseren vergleichbar w\u00e4ren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "181.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "185.240", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Speditionen arbeiten mit undurchsichtigen Gesch\u00e4ftsmodellen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "185.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "188.440", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und das alles auf dem R\u00fccken ihrer Fahrerinnen und Fahrer. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "188.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "191.240", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Fahrerinnen und Fahrer sind teilweise wochen- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "191.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "196.240", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und monatelang unter menschenunw\u00fcrdigen Bedingungen unterwegs. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "196.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "202.560", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der mit diesen Mitteln gef\u00fchrte Wettbewerb \u00fcberlastet Personal und Material massiv. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "202.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "204.560", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Da braucht man sich nicht zu wundern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "204.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "206.800", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass auch die Verkehrssicherheit leidet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "206.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "208.840", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mit fatalen Folgen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "208.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "214.880", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Schreckliche Bilder von Unf\u00e4llen auf Autobahnen haben wir alle vor Augen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "214.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "219.360", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die geschilderten Missst\u00e4nde im Stra\u00dfeng\u00fctertransport, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "219.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "221.160", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "221.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "226.560", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "d\u00fcrfen wir nicht und werden wir Sozialdemokraten zuk\u00fcnftig auch nicht hinnehmen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "226.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "230.440", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Daran werden wir auch auf europ\u00e4ischer Ebene arbeiten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "230.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "233.640", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir m\u00fcssen faire und sozialvertr\u00e4gliche Arbeits- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "233.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "235.400", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Wettbewerbsbedingungen schaffen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "235.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "237.680", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Doch auch die besten Regeln, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "237.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "240.320", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie wir sie gerade in der EU neu diskutieren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "240.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "241.520", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bleiben nutzlos, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "241.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "244.640", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn ihre Einhaltung nicht effektiv kontrolliert wird."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "244.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "249.280", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Von den Fernfahrern auf den Parkpl\u00e4tzen h\u00f6re ich immer wieder: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "249.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "251.080", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gesetze bringen doch eh nichts, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "251.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "253.240", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "man kontrolliert ja nicht.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "253.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "258.560", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im M\u00e4rz wurden in Deutschland zum Beispiel knapp 3\u00a0Milliarden mautpflichtige Kilometer gefahren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "258.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "266.800", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Beim Bundesamt f\u00fcr G\u00fcterverkehr sind derzeit 231\u00a0Mitarbeiter im Stra\u00dfenkontrolldienst besch\u00e4ftigt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "266.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "273.920", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Rein statistisch m\u00fcsste jeder Mitarbeiter mehr als 800\u00a0Lkws am Tag kontrollieren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "273.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "278.600", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist nicht m\u00f6glich und sicherlich am Ende auch nicht n\u00f6tig; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "278.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "281.320", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn eine 100-prozentige Kontrolle gibt es nicht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "281.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "286.200", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber von effektiven Kontrollen sind wir noch ein St\u00fcck weit entfernt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "286.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "287.000", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Darum w\u00fcnsche ich mir\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "287.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "288.840", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dar\u00fcber m\u00fcssen wir diskutieren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "288.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "291.480", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und ich bin davon \u00fcberzeugt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "291.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "294.040", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir es erreichen werden\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "294.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "304.400", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir das Bundesamt f\u00fcr G\u00fcterverkehr deutlich besser aufstellen und auch schon im Rahmen der Haushaltsberatungen\u00a02018 f\u00fcr eine entsprechende personelle und technische Ausstattung sorgen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "304.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "305.680", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "305.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "309.600", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "vielen Dank f\u00fcr Ihre Aufmerksamkeit."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "309.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "311.000", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "311.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "315.000", 
